00:43:06,250 --> 00:43:07,410
高
Cole.

536
00:43:10,670 --> 00:43:12,800
见到你真好，高
Damn nice to see you, Cole.

537
00:43:14,090 --> 00:43:15,190
你好吗？
How you doing, buddy?

538
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:17,880
见到你真好，贝克
It's damn nice to see you, Buck.

539
00:43:18,470 --> 00:43:20,090
你觉得怎样？
How you doing?

540
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:24,180
高，你见过廖医生了
Cole, you've met Dr. Lewicki.

541
00:43:29,190 --> 00:43:30,640
她是你的医生，廖医生
That's your doctor, Dr. Lewicki.

542
00:43:30,690 --> 00:43:33,230
当时他看不见我
I don't think he's actually seen me before.

543
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:34,820
哈利，你又来了
Sure, Harry.

544
00:43:36,490 --> 00:43:38,900
-不  -廖医生
- No... - Dr. Lewicki.

545
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:45,700
医生袍、听筒  这套戏服很逼真
Smock, stethoscope. It's a great costume, Harry.

546
00:43:46,370 --> 00:43:50,580
医生，你好吗？ 高，她真是廖医生
- So how are you, Doc? - No, Cole, this really is Dr. Lewicki.

547
00:43:50,670 --> 00:43:52,750
我本来下班了
I was just about to go off duty.

548
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:55,500
但你想来看看我
You thought you'd come by to look me over.

549
00:43:55,590 --> 00:43:59,630
来检查一下，你恢复视力了？
Well, it's not a bad idea. I figure your vision's restored?

550
00:44:00,380 --> 00:44:01,800
看来是的
I think so.

551
00:44:01,890 --> 00:44:04,310
有没有看到模糊、重迭的影像
Nothing's blurred? You're not seeing double?

552
00:44:04,390 --> 00:44:07,930
有没有看到光晕和闪光？
No haloes around objects? Flashing lights?

553
00:44:09,270 --> 00:44:13,690
慢着，你想做什么？ 看你的眼睛
- What are you going to do with this? - Look into your eyes.

554
00:44:14,270 --> 00:44:16,780
医生
Doc, Doc.

555
00:44:19,360 --> 00:44:22,280
你不是要找这东西吗？
Isn't this what you're really looking for?

556
00:44:25,700 --> 00:44:27,790
很有趣
Well, that's interesting enough, Mr. Trickle,

557
00:44:28,410 --> 00:44:30,370
但这不是我的专科
but it's just not my specialty.

558
00:44:43,010 --> 00:44:44,300
她真的是医生？
She's the real thing?

559
00:44:44,390 --> 00:44:48,220
我怎会在这时候作弄你
Well, I wouldn't play no joke on you in a situation like this.

560
00:44:48,600 --> 00:44:51,270
对不起，我本来也不想笑的
Sorry, Cole, I'm trying not to smile.

561
00:44:51,810 --> 00:44:53,600
给我滚
All right, get out.

562
00:44:55,230 --> 00:44:56,690
走吧…
Get out. Get out of here.

563
00:44:56,770 --> 00:44:58,480
再见
Get some rest, man.

564
00:45:03,860 --> 00:45:05,070
我不对劲
I am not well.

565
00:45:07,410 --> 00:45:08,790
我走得动
I can walk, God damn it.

566
00:45:08,870 --> 00:45:12,040
医院不准你走路
Not as long as you're in this hospital you can't.

567
00:45:15,330 --> 00:45:18,040
我不想见到他，请推快一点
I don't want to be next to this clown. You mind picking up the pace a little?

568
00:45:18,050 --> 00:45:21,880
要药的话，你要找护士
Hey, man, if you want drugs, you have to see the nurse. Okay?

569
00:45:43,450 --> 00:45:44,610
等待
Wait!

570
00:45:58,880 --> 00:46:00,880
我的天
Get out of the way.

571
00:46:07,890 --> 00:46:12,520
早安，两位先生  跟我来
Good morning, gentlemen. Right this way.

572
00:46:17,060 --> 00:46:19,610
班先生和狄先生
So, neither Mr. Burns, nor in this case, Mr. Trickle

573
00:46:19,690 --> 00:46:21,940
颅骨以内都没有受损
present any significant intracranial injury.

574
00:46:22,030 --> 00:46:24,700
慢着，请简单地告诉我
Now hold it, Doc. Let's have that one in English.

575
00:46:24,780 --> 00:46:26,780
他们有没有撞坏脑？
Did they mess up their squash or not?

576
00:46:26,860 --> 00:46:31,080
脑部没有受损  至少跟意外发生前一样
Their brains are intact. As much as they were before the accident anyway.

577
00:46:31,160 --> 00:46:33,330
你准许他们继续赛车？
You're willing to give them clearance to get back on a racetrack?

578
00:46:33,330 --> 00:46:36,000
赛车是危险玩意
Well, that's obviously a dangerous way to spend your time.

579
00:46:36,080 --> 00:46:39,540
我不想听哲学理论  我要医学意见
That's a philosophical objection, Doc, and I'm looking for a medical one.

580
00:46:39,630 --> 00:46:42,000
我暂时不会准许他们赛车
I'm not inclined to give them clearance at this time.

581
00:46:42,090 --> 00:46:45,880
废话  稍安勿躁
- That's total horseshit. - Gentlemen, please.

582
00:46:47,470 --> 00:46:50,220
他们想听取别的医生的意见
I think they're saying they would like another opinion.

583
00:46:50,300 --> 00:46:52,310
我们想见你的上司
We would like to talk to your boss.

584
00:46:52,390 --> 00:46:55,980
你可以这样做  但我和韦医生
You're welcome to, of course, but Dr. Wilhaire and I have consulted

585
00:46:56,060 --> 00:46:58,100
有一致的看法
and we're of the same opinion.

586
00:46:58,190 --> 00:47:00,980
一至两周后再评估他们的情况
Which is a re-evaluation in a week or two.

587
00:47:01,060 --> 00:47:02,160
谢谢，医生
Thank you, Doc.

588
00:47:02,190 --> 00:47:04,190
我想跟他们说话
Now, we have a little something we have to say to the boys here

589
00:47:04,190 --> 00:47:06,420
你不必留下来
and I don't think you necessarily need to hear it.

590
00:47:13,370 --> 00:47:15,580
现在由大哥尊说话
Okay, Big John's turn.

591
00:47:22,090 --> 00:47:24,550
如果你们想撞车死掉
If you wanna turn yourselves into a greasy spot

592
00:47:24,630 --> 00:47:27,380
没问题
on a country road somewhere, go right ahead.

593
00:47:27,470 --> 00:47:29,510
没有人会关心
I don't give a shit and I don't think anybody else does,

594
00:47:29,510 --> 00:47:31,430
你们的死活
regardless of what they say to your face.

595
00:47:31,510 --> 00:47:35,220
但不要在我的赛道生事
But you two monkeys are not going to do it on my racetrack.

596
00:47:36,520 --> 00:47:39,270
你们听过日式检查吗？
Have you all heard of Japanese inspection?

597
00:47:40,100 --> 00:47:41,730
日式检查
Japanese inspection.

598
00:47:41,810 --> 00:47:43,730
日本人
You see, when the Japs get in a load of lettuce

599
00:47:43,730 --> 00:47:46,360
不想外国生菜进口
that they're not sure they want to let in the country,

600
00:47:46,440 --> 00:47:48,400
他们让生菜搁在码头
why, they just let it sit on the docks

601
00:47:48,490 --> 00:47:51,110
日后才去检查
until they get good and ready to look at it.

602
00:47:51,240 --> 00:47:55,740
后来所有生菜都腐坏了
By then of course, it's all gone rotten. Ain't nothing left to inspect.

603
00:47:55,870 --> 00:47:59,540
生菜是容易腐坏的货品
In other words, lettuce is a perishable item

604
00:48:00,750 --> 00:48:02,630
你们也一样
like you two monkeys.

605
00:48:02,880 --> 00:48:05,630
如果你们再互相碰撞
You trade paint one more time, you so much as touch,

606
00:48:05,710 --> 00:48:07,760
我会取消你们的资格
I'm gonna black-flag the two of you.

607
00:48:07,840 --> 00:48:10,800
没收跑车
Gonna take apart your racecar for 300 laps.

608
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:12,340
等你们通过健康检查
Then if you pass the inspection,

609
00:48:12,340 --> 00:48:16,770
重造跑车  我可能会让你们出赛
and you put your car back together, I might let you get back in the race.

610
00:48:17,060 --> 00:48:19,850
你们要冰释前嫌
Now, just to show us there's no hard feelings,

611
00:48:19,940 --> 00:48:22,400
今晚一起吃晚饭
we're all gonna go out to dinner together.

612
00:48:22,480 --> 00:48:25,020
-我有别的约会  -我也一样
- I've got other plans. - Yeah, and so do I.

613
00:48:25,110 --> 00:48:27,440
取消约会
Well, you're gonna have to change them.

614
00:48:27,530 --> 00:48:31,200
你们要一起开车去餐厅
And not only that, you two are gonna drive to dinner together.

615
00:48:39,160 --> 00:48:40,660
廖医生
Dr. Lewicki.

616
00:48:41,290 --> 00:48:43,830
我想为高
I want to apologize for what happened with Cole

617
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:46,630
的行为道歉
when you come into the hospital room.

618
00:48:46,710 --> 00:48:49,800
霍先生，不必介怀
Mr. Hogge, please, it's nothing to worry about.

619
00:48:49,880 --> 00:48:52,510
你没有做错
And in any case it was hardly your doing.

620
00:48:52,590 --> 00:48:54,470
我要负上责任
Well, that's just it, I believe it was.

621
00:48:54,550 --> 00:48:57,970
不久前，狄高赢了达令顿大赛
You see, not too long ago after he won Darlington,

622
00:48:58,060 --> 00:49:00,060
我们捉弄他
we played a trick on Cole.

623
00:49:00,600 --> 00:49:04,690
我们找一位美女扮作公路女警
We dressed up a pretty girl in a highway-patrol uniform.

624
00:49:04,810 --> 00:49:10,610
我们请她挑逗狄高
Anyway, we told her to get real ornery with him and she did.

625
00:49:11,240 --> 00:49:14,240
你的意思是…  她真的挑逗狄高
- By ornery, you mean... - I mean, real ornery.

626
00:49:16,830 --> 00:49:19,620
为什么告诉我这件事？
Why would you want me to know about this?

627
00:49:20,370 --> 00:49:22,830
我不想你对高起了反感
I don't want you to hold a bad opinion of Cole.

628
00:49:22,910 --> 00:49:24,960
他会害怕
I believe it scares him.

629
00:49:26,340 --> 00:49:29,210
他需要你给他信心
He needs reassurance from you that he's okay.

630
00:49:29,300 --> 00:49:33,380
毕竟你是他的医生
After all, you're his doctor.

631
00:49:38,180 --> 00:49:39,510
我说完了
That's it.

632
00:49:59,700 --> 00:50:00,910
医生
Doc.

633
00:50:02,450 --> 00:50:05,710
有人说你误会我是公路女警
I heard you thought I was a highway-patrol officer.

634
00:50:08,290 --> 00:50:10,840
谢谢你照顾我
I also want to thank you for taking care of me.

635
00:50:10,920 --> 00:50:12,460
那是我的职责
It's my job.

636
00:50:13,550 --> 00:50:15,130
你救了我
It's my life.

637
00:50:16,470 --> 00:50:19,430
这次我们握手吧
Well, this time let's shake hands.

638
00:50:19,510 --> 00:50:22,470
好  祝你好运  对不起
- Of course. Of course. - Good luck, Cole.

639
00:50:31,400 --> 00:50:36,320
廖医生  我可以再见你吗？ 你一定会再见到我
- Dr. Lewicki, could I see you? - You will, I promise.

640
00:50:36,860 --> 00:50:38,030
我的意思是…
No, I mean,

641
00:50:38,120 --> 00:50:41,580
一起吃饭、看戏  我带你看赛车
have some dinner, go catch a movie. I'll take you to a race.

642
00:50:42,080 --> 00:50:44,290
谢谢你邀请我
That's very sweet, really,

643
00:50:44,370 --> 00:50:47,210
但我不会让你提早回跑道赛车
but it won't get you back on the track any faster.

644
00:50:48,040 --> 00:50:52,500
不是…  我没有这想法
No, it's not what I meant.

645
00:51:15,940 --> 00:51:19,490
你想怎样？ 我们要解决一个问题
- You got me here, now what? - Here's how I see this deal.

646
00:51:19,570 --> 00:51:22,870
我不会让你开车去餐厅
Since you agree I ain't gonna let you drive this car to dinner

647
00:51:22,950 --> 00:51:25,630
你也不会让我开车去餐厅
and I agree you ain't gonna let me drive this car to dinner,

648
00:51:25,660 --> 00:51:27,580
只有一个解决方法
there's only one way to settle this.

649
00:51:27,660 --> 00:51:29,790
你说什么？
What are you talking about?

650
00:51:32,380 --> 00:51:34,540
(汽车出租)

651
00:51:34,710 --> 00:51:36,260
好主意
Absolutely.

652
00:52:16,710 --> 00:52:19,010
添，听着
Let me tell you something, Tim.

653
00:52:20,180 --> 00:52:23,350
如果你不能管束你的车手
If you can't control your race drivers any better than this,

654
00:52:25,260 --> 00:52:28,060
你还是别做领队好了
you might consider sticking to something you can control.

655
00:52:30,770 --> 00:52:33,400
回沙洛特-加龙省卖二手车吧
Like used cars in downtown Charlotte.

656
00:52:55,960 --> 00:52:59,010
不算太迟
- Too close to call? - Yeah.

657
00:53:10,600 --> 00:53:15,270
你迟到了  车有毛病
- You're late. - We had car trouble.

658
00:53:16,270 --> 00:53:18,280
什么毛病？
What kind of car trouble?

659
00:53:18,860 --> 00:53:22,400
是水箱有问题，对不对？
I believe it was the radiator. Wasn't it, Cole?

660
00:53:23,410 --> 00:53:25,620
对，该是这样
Yes, Rowdy, I believe it was.

661
00:53:33,750 --> 00:53:36,840
添，你认识医院的职员吗？
Tim, do you know anybody at Daytona Memorial?

662
00:53:36,920 --> 00:53:39,670
认识院长，为什么？ 他是不是赛车迷？
- The chief of staff. Why? - Is he a race fan?

663
00:53:39,750 --> 00:53:41,010
对不起
He was born in the South.

664
00:53:41,090 --> 00:53:43,130
添想你和韦鲁斯见见面
Tim wanted you to meet Russ Wheeler.

665
00:53:43,220 --> 00:53:46,430
他会暂时代替你为车队出赛
He's gonna be driving for us till you get your medical clearance.

666
00:53:46,510 --> 00:53:48,810
我感到很荣幸，狄先生
It's a real pleasure to race your car, Mr. Trickle.

667
00:53:48,890 --> 00:53:50,470
谢谢你来帮忙
Yeah, thanks for helping out.

668
00:53:50,560 --> 00:53:55,440
添…  我想知道一位医生的住址
Yeah, Tim, I need a home address of a doctor...

669
00:53:55,520 --> 00:53:57,380
我的驾驶技术
I'm only sorry I won't be able to drive it

670
00:53:57,400 --> 00:53:59,730
比不上你
nearly as good as you though.

671
00:54:01,780 --> 00:54:03,780
哈利，待会见
I'll see you later, Harry.

672
00:54:05,070 --> 00:54:07,160
医院那位医生…
Yeah, the doctor that...

673
00:54:09,280 --> 00:54:10,540
那位…
That...

674
00:54:13,500 --> 00:54:14,620
什么？
What?

675
00:54:32,310 --> 00:54:34,940
我很想吸引你注意
I was desperate to get your attention.

676
00:54:36,770 --> 00:54:39,610
你成功了，我的家变成森林
Well, you got it. I walked into a jungle.

677
00:54:41,020 --> 00:54:46,860
很美丽…但我不能来  我是医生，我得随时应诊
No, it's nicely extravagant, but really, I can't. I'm a doctor on call.

678
00:54:47,450 --> 00:54:51,080
我是病人  我和洛甸要检受检查
And I'm a patient. Somebody has to re-examine me. I need clearance.

679
00:54:51,330 --> 00:54:53,040
来检查我们，我带你看赛车
Come up here and do that. I'll take you to a race.

680
00:54:53,040 --> 00:54:56,210
我不想浪费假期
Come on, I don't want to watch you guys going round and round in circles,

681
00:54:56,210 --> 00:54:59,170
看你们打圈追逐
chasing each other like a pack of dogs on my day off.

682
00:54:59,250 --> 00:55:01,960
那你放假来追逐我吧
Then how about chasing me on your day off?

683
00:55:02,050 --> 00:55:05,470
我没有假期，我要24小时应诊
I don't have a day off. I'm on call 24 hours.

684
00:55:05,550 --> 00:55:09,340
医生，假设你有两天假期…
Okay, Doctor, let's suppose you had a couple of days off...

685
00:55:09,430 --> 00:55:11,300
糖…
Sugar. Sugar.

686
00:55:11,390 --> 00:55:13,350
又没有什么节目
...with nothing else to do.

687
00:55:13,430 --> 00:55:17,310
你想不想来北卡罗来纳？
Could I interest you in the North Carolina countryside?

688
00:55:17,560 --> 00:55:20,980
这是假设？ 只是假设
- Speaking theoretically? - Speaking theoretically.

689
00:55:21,060 --> 00:55:24,320
可能吧，你得说服我上司
Maybe. But you'd have to convince my boss.

690
00:55:24,400 --> 00:55:28,320
好…你有多高？
Good. Good. How tall are you?

691
00:55:44,420 --> 00:55:45,960
他说什么？
What did he say?

692
00:55:46,050 --> 00:55:49,430
医生，到沙洛特-加龙省  检查那两个小子
"Doctor, fly to Charlotte and check those boys out."

693
00:55:53,140 --> 00:55:56,020
我的天  你迫不及待
Boy, you're very quick.

694
00:55:57,640 --> 00:55:59,690
你应该看看我赛车
You ought to see me drive.

695
00:56:04,110 --> 00:56:05,210
洛甸不在这里
Rowdy's not here.

696
00:56:05,280 --> 00:56:08,700
我叫他五时来找我们
Well, I told him to meet us at the infield by 5:00.

697
00:56:08,780 --> 00:56:12,200
我先替高检查吧
Well, we should probably get started on Cole.

698
00:56:16,580 --> 00:56:19,460
闭上眼睛  手掌向上
Close your eyes. Palms up.

699
00:56:21,710 --> 00:56:24,960
张开眼睛  垂下双手
Open your eyes. Arms down.

700
00:56:26,340 --> 00:56:28,010
看着我的手指
Follow my finger.

701
00:56:43,810 --> 00:56:46,980
站立，双脚靠拢，闭上眼睛
Stand with your feet together and close your eyes.

702
00:56:50,450 --> 00:56:54,780
踏前一步  张开眼睛
Walk one foot in front of the other. Open your eyes.

703
00:56:56,450 --> 00:56:58,290
回桌子
And back on the table.

704
00:57:06,090 --> 00:57:07,630
真难受
This is tough.

705
00:57:08,130 --> 00:57:10,760
-检查总是难受的  -为什么？
- Examinations always are. - Why's that?

706
00:57:11,380 --> 00:57:15,300
因为我可能会发现坏现象
Because I'm looking you over and I might not like what I see.

707
00:57:15,390 --> 00:57:19,310
你会担心  凝视墙壁
That has to worry you. Pick a spot on the wall and look at it.

708
00:57:24,690 --> 00:57:27,110
-别动  -我没有动
- Please, don't move. Your eyes. - I didn't move.

709
00:57:27,190 --> 00:57:29,110
眼睛固定注视一个地方
Just focus on one spot.

710
00:57:39,370 --> 00:57:42,790
你在看什么？ 视网膜
- What do you see? - The retina.

711
00:57:44,290 --> 00:57:46,210
它怎样？
What does it look like?

712
00:57:49,590 --> 00:57:51,510
很美丽
Very pretty, actually.

713
00:57:59,140 --> 00:58:01,220
看够了吗？ 差不多了
