Let me out of the car, Cole. Let me out of the car.

885
01:12:46,650 --> 01:12:49,950
我要下车  你不停车我也要下车
Let me out of the car! Let me out or I'm getting out.

886
01:12:50,900 --> 01:12:52,360
嘿…
Hey! Hey, hey!

887
01:12:53,990 --> 01:12:57,540
嘉莉  别走
Claire! Wait. Just wait.

888
01:12:57,620 --> 01:12:59,370
别跟着来，我会报警
- Get away or I'll call the police. - You'll what?

889
01:12:59,370 --> 01:13:01,620
-什么？ -你听到的  报警吧
- You heard me. - Okay, call the police.

890
01:13:01,710 --> 01:13:02,870
我会跟着你等你说话
But I'm not leaving until you talk.

891
01:13:02,880 --> 01:13:04,540
-我无话可说  -我有话要说
- I've got nothing to say. - Well, I do!

892
01:13:04,540 --> 01:13:06,800
好，说吧
Okay, great. Let's hear it.

893
01:13:10,340 --> 01:13:12,430
就是这样？好
- That's it? Fine. - Just...

894
01:13:12,510 --> 01:13:15,680
-来吧  -你不应该开车  不要再去马路、跑道
You shouldn't be driving a car anyway. Not on a road, not on a racetrack,

895
01:13:15,680 --> 01:13:16,850
以及停车场
and not in a parking lot.

896
01:13:16,930 --> 01:13:20,310
你自私、疯狂，你害怕
You're selfish, you're crazy and you're scared.

897
01:13:20,390 --> 01:13:22,600
我没有害怕  你怕得要死
- I'm not scared. - You are scared to death.

898
01:13:22,690 --> 01:13:25,230
你和洛甸一样
You and Rowdy, you have the same sickness. It's called denial.

899
01:13:25,230 --> 01:13:28,070
不肯面对现实迟早会没命
And it's probably going to kill you both.

900
01:13:32,910 --> 01:13:34,570
你说你想控制
You want to control something that's out of control,

901
01:13:34,570 --> 01:13:36,870
无法控制的局面
that's what you said to me, wasn't it?

902
01:13:36,950 --> 01:13:38,330
让我告诉你
I'm going to let you in on a little secret

903
01:13:38,330 --> 01:13:41,250
所有人都知道…
that almost everybody else in this world automatically knows.

904
01:13:41,330 --> 01:13:44,000
我们不能控制
Control is an illusion, you infantile egomaniac.

905
01:13:44,080 --> 01:13:46,540
也无法预知未来
Nobody knows what's gonna happen next.

906
01:13:46,630 --> 01:13:49,630
车、飞机、我们的身体  随时会出事
Not on a freeway, not in an airplane, not inside our own bodies,

907
01:13:49,710 --> 01:13:53,760
四十个自大狂一起飚车  自然更危险
and certainly not on a racetrack with 40 other infantile egomaniacs.

908
01:13:53,840 --> 01:13:55,930
没有人能控制任何事
Nobody knows and nobody controls anything.

909
01:13:56,010 --> 01:13:58,560
你意识到这道理，于是你害怕
Now, you've gotten a glimpse of that and you're scared.

910
01:13:58,640 --> 01:14:00,220
你失去勇气
You might not have the courage to race anymore.

911
01:14:00,220 --> 01:14:02,270
你再不能赛车
You may never have had it.

912
01:14:06,520 --> 01:14:08,060
你真讨厌
God, I hate you for this, you son of a bitch.

913
01:14:08,070 --> 01:14:10,440
你逼我板起面孔说教
You make me sound like a doctor.

914
01:15:05,210 --> 01:15:06,540
珍妮
Jennie.

915
01:15:08,500 --> 01:15:10,170
你为什么来了？
Why are you here?

916
01:15:12,710 --> 01:15:14,130
他在哪里？
Where is he?

917
01:15:26,770 --> 01:15:29,230
-听说你失业了  -对
- I hear you're out of a job. - Yeah.

918
01:15:34,860 --> 01:15:37,030
你脸色很差
You're not looking too good.

919
01:15:39,110 --> 01:15:41,660
一天吃多少颗止痛药？
How many of these things do you chew every day?

920
01:15:41,740 --> 01:15:43,870
你来做什么？
What did you come here for?

921
01:15:46,830 --> 01:15:49,000
抓你去医院
To take you to the hospital.

922
01:15:52,340 --> 01:15:54,340
若不是那个女医生
If it had been anybody but a damn woman doctor,

923
01:15:54,340 --> 01:15:57,340
我早已回去赛车
I'd have been back on the track weeks ago.

924
01:15:57,420 --> 01:16:00,180
是吗？ 是
- Is that right? - Yeah, that's right.

925
01:16:00,260 --> 01:16:04,060
听着  断腿、心脏受伤
Listen, man, I've raced with my legs broke, heart bruised,

926
01:16:04,140 --> 01:16:07,390
眼球快掉出来
eyes popping out of my head like they're on springs.

927
01:16:08,060 --> 01:16:11,230
我还不是照样参赛
This is going to go away just like anything else.

928
01:16:11,360 --> 01:16:13,440
这次也不会例外  我不会死
As far as I'm concerned, I'm going to live forever,

929
01:16:13,440 --> 01:16:15,860
去了医院才会死
unless I go to some damn hospital where they

930
01:16:15,940 --> 01:16:20,450
他们逼你脱鞋、闭上眼睛  然后你就死了
take your shoes off, and make you shut your eyes, and bang, you're dead.

931
01:16:21,620 --> 01:16:23,660
这是什么奖杯？
What did you win this for?

932
01:16:24,490 --> 01:16:27,580
这个…是那场赛事的？
This one right here. What did you win this for?

933
01:16:29,120 --> 01:16:30,920
上面没写着吗？
Doesn't it say?

934
01:16:31,080 --> 01:16:32,500
温斯顿杯
Yeah, it's the Winston Cup, buddy.

935
01:16:32,500 --> 01:16:35,380
容易被人遗忘
Well, hell, that's an easy one to forget.

936
01:16:35,500 --> 01:16:38,880
你的名字呢？你也忘了？
What's your name? Or has that slipped your mind, too?

937
01:16:42,390 --> 01:16:44,890
去你的
- Screw you, man. - Okay.

938
01:16:45,760 --> 01:16:48,770
去医院治好你的脑袋  或者留在这里敲脑袋
We can go down there and fix your head or we can fix it right here!

939
01:16:48,890 --> 01:16:50,850
你选哪一样？
Now, what's it gonna be?

940
01:16:56,730 --> 01:16:58,900
洛甸想见你
Rowdy would like to see you.

941
01:17:05,330 --> 01:17:07,450
-他怎样？ -他还好
- How is he? - He's okay.

942
01:17:08,700 --> 01:17:10,790
-你好吗？ -很好
- How are you? - Good.

943
01:17:12,540 --> 01:17:14,960
他能否参加地通拿赛？
Think he'll make Daytona? It's not for a few months.

944
01:17:15,040 --> 01:17:16,630
他会康复
I think he'll make it out of the hospital.

945
01:17:16,630 --> 01:17:20,010
但他再不能赛车
But he'll never drive a racecar again.

946
01:17:27,260 --> 01:17:30,930
这是韦医生，他替洛甸施手术
Cole, this is Dr. Wilhaire. He's going to be doing the surgery.

947
01:17:31,060 --> 01:17:32,890
-我是狄高  -狄高
- Cole Trickle. - Cole.

948
01:17:33,850 --> 01:17:35,400
他怎样？
So, how is he?

949
01:17:36,400 --> 01:17:39,860
医生说我的脑部要动小手术
Well, the doc here says I need minor brain surgery.

950
01:17:39,940 --> 01:17:41,670
也不算是小手术
Well, that's not exactly how I put it.

951
01:17:41,700 --> 01:17:45,700
他脑袋太小，只能动小手术
Well, listen, Doc, any surgery on his brain is bound to be minor.

952
01:17:47,530 --> 01:17:49,830
我想跟他单独谈谈
You all mind if I talk to this guy a second?

953
01:17:49,910 --> 01:17:51,290
好
Of course.

954
01:18:02,800 --> 01:18:06,010
脑部有一条血管爆裂了
They say I got a busted blood vessel in my brain.

955
01:18:06,090 --> 01:18:10,600
他们想在我的头开洞取瘀血
So, they want to drill a hole in my head and get rid of the leaky blood.

956
01:18:12,100 --> 01:18:14,940
我应该接受手术吗？
You think I should let them do it, Cole?

957
01:18:15,940 --> 01:18:17,230
应该
Yeah.

958
01:18:17,310 --> 01:18:20,980
换了是你，你会动手术？ 我会
- You'd let them if it was you? - I would.

959
01:18:21,690 --> 01:18:25,200
好，我想请你帮我做一件事
Okay, then I've got to ask you to do something for me.

960
01:18:26,240 --> 01:18:27,740
说吧
Well, name it.

961
01:18:27,820 --> 01:18:31,700
驾驶我的车  你说什么？
- Drive my car. - What are you talking about?

962
01:18:31,790 --> 01:18:33,040
地通拿大赛
Daytona.

963
01:18:36,040 --> 01:18:38,250
你有足够时间准备出赛
No, Rowdy, you have plenty of time to get ready for Daytona.

964
01:18:38,250 --> 01:18:39,960
不必找我
You don't need me.

965
01:18:42,010 --> 01:18:45,800
我失去了赞助商  他们没有赞助我的跑车
I lost my sponsor. They put their money on me, not the car.

966
01:18:45,880 --> 01:18:49,600
我不知道手术会否成功
Now, they ain't too sure I'm going to come out of this deal.

967
01:18:50,100 --> 01:18:51,350
你说呢？
Are you?

968
01:18:54,890 --> 01:18:58,770
我买了地，还没付钱
I've got a lot of land and a lot of plans I ain't paid for.

969
01:18:58,860 --> 01:19:02,440
我的车要胜出
So the only way to get my sponsor back is to make sure

970
01:19:02,530 --> 01:19:04,070
才会有赞助商找我
my car runs good at Daytona.

971
01:19:04,150 --> 01:19:06,660
电视台会注意我的车
All that network TV shit, you know.

972
01:19:07,950 --> 01:19:09,050
不必找我
Well, you don't need me.

973
01:19:09,120 --> 01:19:10,950
这里还有其他车手
There's plenty of other drivers. You don't need me.

974
01:19:10,950 --> 01:19:14,450
别来这一套，混蛋
Don't give me that mealy-mouthed shit, you son of a bitch.

975
01:19:14,540 --> 01:19:17,250
我要找一个能登上五甲的车手
I got to put a driver in my car that'll finish in the top five,

976
01:19:17,250 --> 01:19:20,670
否则赞助商不会为我付账
before my sponsors will pick up the tab for the year.

977
01:19:21,920 --> 01:19:25,380
地通拿大赛后我可能会复出
Maybe after Daytona, maybe I can drive.

978
01:19:26,880 --> 01:19:28,180
也可能无法复出
Maybe it'll be a different driver.

979
01:19:28,180 --> 01:19:31,300
现在我要想办法养家
But in the meantime, I want the best for my family.

980
01:19:31,390 --> 01:19:34,060
别推搪我
So don't you bullshit me, Cole.

981
01:19:34,140 --> 01:19:38,560
你有什么理由不替我出赛？
Is there some other reason why I ain't good enough for you to drive for?

982
01:19:49,160 --> 01:19:50,820
你答应我了？
Then you'll do it?

983
01:20:04,960 --> 01:20:08,090
还以为你不肯帮我
Shit, man. You had me going.

984
01:20:09,840 --> 01:20:14,060
现在谈细节吧  你和杜添签了什么合约？
Now, let's get down to business here. What's your deal with Daland?

985
01:20:17,270 --> 01:20:20,730
我们改天再谈吧  失陪一会
Hell, we'll work that out, okay? Excuse me for a second.

986
01:20:26,030 --> 01:20:29,360
高，什么事？ 告诉洛甸我会给他电话
- Cole, what's wrong? - Just tell Rowdy I'll call him.

987
01:20:47,090 --> 01:20:49,510
不行…
No, no, no, no, sir!

988
01:20:49,630 --> 01:20:52,890
不能合作，不想合作  代价太大
Can't use them. Don't want them. Couldn't afford them if I did.

989
01:20:52,970 --> 01:20:54,640
你说什么？
What the hell are you talking about?

990
01:20:54,720 --> 01:20:58,390
我说赛车手  我知道你和班洛甸的事
Racecar drivers. I know all about you and Rowdy Burns.

991
01:20:58,480 --> 01:21:02,560
我不会为你们修车参赛
And I ain't setting up that car for Daytona or anywhere else, Cole,

992
01:21:02,650 --> 01:21:04,440
但你可以进来
but you're welcome to come on in.

993
01:21:04,520 --> 01:21:06,650
我们喝酒、瞎扯
We'll bring out the moonshine and start telling lies

994
01:21:06,650 --> 01:21:08,030
同时找美人
and calling up the women.

995
01:21:08,110 --> 01:21:12,200
赛车免谈，进来  好，不谈赛车
- But no talk about racing. Come on. - All right, no talk about racing.

996
01:21:12,280 --> 01:21:13,740
贝克，来
Come on, Buck,

997
01:21:14,450 --> 01:21:16,240
我跟你们赛跑
I'll race your ass.

998
01:21:29,340 --> 01:21:32,470
我要走了，晚安
I believe I'm gonna take off. Good night, Harry.

999
01:21:46,150 --> 01:21:48,400
为什么不帮我？
Why won't you set up the car?

1000
01:21:53,490 --> 01:21:56,580
自从那次意外中洛甸受伤后
Ever since you and Rowdy crashed at Daytona and Rowdy got sick,

1001
01:21:56,660 --> 01:21:58,530
你担心自己
you've been waiting for the other shoe to drop,

1002
01:21:58,540 --> 01:22:01,370
也会遇上不幸
waiting on something bad to happen to you.

1003
01:22:03,040 --> 01:22:05,080
他们说白毕地经常听到怪声
Just like Buddy Bretherton. He started hearing voices.

1004
01:22:05,080 --> 01:22:08,710
在哪个赛车场都听到
All kinds of them, everywhere. Atlanta, Richmond, Wilkesboro.

1005
01:22:08,800 --> 01:22:11,670
他听到一个讯息
And all of them only had but one thing to say,

1006
01:22:11,760 --> 01:22:15,930
离开跑车，下车…
"Get out of that racecar. Get out..."

1007
01:22:21,810 --> 01:22:23,270
在亚特兰大
You pegged the engine in Atlanta,

1008
01:22:23,270 --> 01:22:25,770
你把引擎烧坏
redlined the son of a bitch and blew it sky-high.

1009
01:22:25,850 --> 01:22:28,690
你是故意的
Done it deliberate. Done it deliberate.

1010
01:22:30,150 --> 01:22:34,820
转数标指着9400转
9,400 rpms according to the little telltale button.

1011
01:22:37,370 --> 01:22:41,200
你不想赛车，你不想死
You was worried if you didn't get out of that car right quick, you'd die.

1012
01:22:41,290 --> 01:22:43,080
我有没有说错了
Now call me a liar.

1013
01:22:44,620 --> 01:22:46,370
你没说错
You're not lying.

1014
01:22:46,460 --> 01:22:50,170
现在你还要谈什么？
All right. What the hell are we talking about then?

1015
01:22:50,250 --> 01:22:54,090
我想开洛甸的车参赛  你要帮我
Racing Rowdy's car at Daytona. I can't do it without you.

1016
01:22:54,800 --> 01:22:56,760
你是干不来的
You can't do it period.

1017
01:22:59,010 --> 01:23:01,560
我不会重返赛车场
And I ain't going back there, Cole.

1018
01:23:12,900 --> 01:23:16,200
白毕地不是死于心脏病  对吗？ 什么？
Buddy didn't really die of a heart attack, did he?

1019
01:23:16,990 --> 01:23:20,530
白毕地不是死于心脏病吧
Buddy didn't really die of a heart attack, did he?

1020
01:23:20,620 --> 01:23:23,910
真相你还是不知道的好
No, he didn't, but you don't wanna hear about it.

1021
01:23:27,290 --> 01:23:31,460
赛车会相信  是跑车的装置害死了他
NASCAR privately claimed the setup on the car is what killed Buddy.

1022
01:23:35,260 --> 01:23:37,590
你用薄气喉来减轻车身重量
You used thin-walled tubing to keep the weight down.

1023
01:23:37,680 --> 01:23:39,890
气喉爆裂
The exhaust fumes broke through the fire wall

1024
01:23:39,970 --> 01:23:42,350
毕地吸入一氧化碳
and carbon monoxide knocked Buddy out.

1025
01:23:42,470 --> 01:23:45,100
废话  撞墙的时候
Horseshit! When Buddy hit the wall at the third turn,

1026
01:23:45,180 --> 01:23:48,190
他还是嚷个不停
he was jabbering on the radio about as fast as he was driving.

1027
01:23:48,270 --> 01:23:50,690
什么一氧化碳
Carbon monoxide, my ass.

1028
01:23:50,770 --> 01:23:52,650
昏迷的人
That was the loudest-talking unconscious man

1029
01:23:52,650 --> 01:23:53,920
怎会说话
you ever heard in your life.

1030
01:23:53,940 --> 01:23:56,990
毕地胡思乱想，结果送命
Nothing killed Buddy but his imagination.

1031
01:23:57,070 --> 01:24:00,570
为什么不让他们调查死因  为什么？
Why didn't you let them investigate, Harry? Why? Why?

1032
01:24:02,200 --> 01:24:03,200
因为我早应该
'Cause I should have known better

1033
01:24:03,280 --> 01:24:06,120
阻止他参赛
than to let him drive in the first place.

1034
01:24:07,830 --> 01:24:09,790
白毕地
You see, Buddy...

1035
01:24:09,870 --> 01:24:12,840
最惹人讨厌
Buddy was a terrible pain in the ass. He really was.

1036
01:24:12,920 --> 01:24:14,590
他自认对车有认识
He thought he knew about cars,

1037
01:24:14,670 --> 01:24:17,010
所以他比你更无知
which made him twice as ignorant as you.

1038
01:24:18,880 --> 01:24:20,340
但是…
But still...

1039
01:24:26,890 --> 01:24:29,770
我看着他赛车
I look at guys like Buddy...

1040
01:24:29,850 --> 01:24:34,570
他可以把跑车发挥得淋漓尽致
I've seen him do things in my racecar that's absolutely unbelievable.

1041
01:24:34,650 --> 01:24:37,320
证明我没有枉费心机
That really showed me what I had done.

1042
01:24:38,280 --> 01:24:39,380
你会不自觉地
And then you see,

1043
01:24:39,450 --> 01:24:42,490
爱上他这类人
you're gonna automatically have to sort of love that guy.

1044
01:24:42,570 --> 01:24:44,700
不论你喜不喜欢他
Whether you want to or not.

1045
01:24:46,750 --> 01:24:48,410
白毕地
Buddy Bretherton.

1046
01:24:50,920 --> 01:24:53,460
哈利，我想问你一件事
I have to ask you something, Harry.

1047
01:24:54,130 --> 01:24:59,300
在撞墙之前
Now, before Buddy hit the wall,

1048
01:24:59,380 --> 01:25:02,180
毕地在赛道上表现如何？
how was he actually doing in that race?

1049
01:25:03,180 --> 01:25:07,140
该死的
- You ornery, no good... - Hey, hey...

1050
01:25:07,220 --> 01:25:11,440
我那部车就看你的了
You set up that car. You set up the car.

1051
01:25:11,520 --> 01:25:15,570
不要再赛车，你会死  你会死，听到吗？ 你会死
If you get back in that car, you'll die. You'll die. You hear?

1052
01:25:19,900 --> 01:25:23,570
我不开我的车，我开洛甸的车
I'm not getting back in my car, I'm getting in Rowdy's.

1053
01:25:23,660 --> 01:25:26,870
你真是蠢得可怜
Well, I see how you're dumb enough to be a race driver.

1054
01:25:26,950 --> 01:25:29,270
开他的车就可以避过厄运？
You think you'll hide from your bad luck in his car?

1055
01:25:29,330 --> 01:25:31,370
何必为洛甸冒险？
What the hell for? For Rowdy?

1056
